mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Kh%E1%BB%91c-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-T%C3%B4n-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-u4a873F30pkHItn208dJvw">Khốc Trường Tôn thị ngự - 哭長孫侍禦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Lam-Quan-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-LeacmClGyb7kQhmRgJxPFA">Lam Quan hoài cổ - 藍關懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BA%AFc-hi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-VYasO4wFAO6exBskUh6-Qw">Nhập tắc hiếu - 入則孝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Ph%C3%A0n-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-tam-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-ph%C3%B3-H%C3%A1n-Trung-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-gV8W2jkzRYVUPWD3eyzNhQ">Tống Phàn nhị thập tam thị ngự phó Hán Trung phán quan - 送樊二十三侍御赴漢中判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
